and clarify what\ningredients of the quantum experiment must be missing in any classical model\nthat can reproduce the anomaly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 18:23:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 14:07:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-23"}
