 in the range of 1--3 m s$^{-1}$ , with the largest\nvalues for $m\\sim10$. No evidence for the $m=2$ sectoral mode is found in the\npower spectrum, implying that the rms velocity of this mode is below $\\sim$0.5\nm s$^{-1}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2018 14:55:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2019 20:59:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 2 Mar 2019 16:57:47 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 29 Apr 2019 16:32:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-05"}
